1
00:00:30,190 --> 00:00:30,960
Chun'er.

2
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,420
Ako ay pinagtaksilan ni Huan Huan

3
00:00:33,710 --> 00:00:35,640
at nawalan ng kontrol sa Great Yan.

4
00:00:36,390 --> 00:00:37,960
Sana matulungan mo ako

5
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:39,840
bawiin mo si Great Yan.

6
00:00:42,710 --> 00:00:44,200
Bakit kita tutulungan?

7
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:47,600
Ikaw ay walang iba kundi isang inabandunang sangla ngayon.

8
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,870
Anuman ang iniisip mo,

9
00:01:16,870 --> 00:01:17,930
Susubukan ko.

10
00:01:18,710 --> 00:01:19,920
Kaya kong gawin ang lahat,

11
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:22,070
kahit na ito ay nangangahulugan ng panganib sa aking buhay.

12
00:01:22,070 --> 00:01:23,310
Tulungan mo lang ako.

13
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,780
Nadumihan mo na ito.

14
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,760
ayoko na.

15
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:34,490
ako ngayon
isang makapangyarihang Prinsesang Tagapagtanggol ng Estado.

16
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,920
Kung gusto mo akong makita,

17
00:01:36,310 --> 00:01:39,370
pumunta sa Mansion ng Prinsesa
para humiling ng audience.

18
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:19,440
[MULI NA PAGSILANG]

19
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:22,430
[Episode 35]

20
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:26,000
[Mansion ng Prinsesa]

21
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,120
Sabi ng aming Prinsesa

22
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,800
kung gusto mo siyang makita,

23
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:38,150
dapat lumuhod ka dito ng 24 oras

24
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,020
upang magkaroon ng karangalan sa pagpasok.

25
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:50,430
Sabi din ng ating Prinsesa

26
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,120
siya lang...

27
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,720
sinusubukan kang takutin.

28
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,000
-Para takutin ka.
-Para takutin ka.

29
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,530
Binigyan ka niya ng 4 na oras.

30
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:58,390
-Apat.
-Apat.

31
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,560
Sumunod ka sa akin.

32
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:05,560
Yan Xun.

33
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:07,630
alam mo ba

34
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,360
Dati gusto talaga kita.

35
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,190
Pero sinira mo ako.

36
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:19,160
Wala akong nararamdaman sayo ngayon.

37
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,160
Bakit kita tutulungan?

38
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,040
Chun'er.

39
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,070
Wala akong kapangyarihan ngayon.

40
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,830
Ang kinabukasan ng Great Yan ay nasa panganib.

41
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:34,050
Kung mabibigyan mo ako ng 5,000 sundalo,

42
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:36,510
Kaya kong bawiin si Great Yan.

43
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,820
Hangga't payag ka,

44
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:41,870
Handa akong tubusin ang lahat

45
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,270
sa nakaraan.

46
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,000
Ganoon ba?

47
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:59,330
Payag ka ba talaga
para gumawa ng kahit ano para sa akin?

48
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,120
ako ay.

49
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,840
Magpalit sa mga damit na ito.

50
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,510
Teka.

51
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,590
Magpalit ka na dito.

52
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,160
Li Yan.

53
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,800
Chun'er.

54
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,750
miss na miss na kita.

55
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,480
Li Yan.

56
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,310
Hindi.

57
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:27,520
Ang mga kilay na ito ay hindi mukhang
iginuhit niya ang mga ito!

58
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,630
Chun'er.

59
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:32,000
Chun'er.

60
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:47,960
Chun'er!

61
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:49,120
Chun'er!

62
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:53,780
♪ Ang alikabok sa mundo ♪

63
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,240
Chun'er.

64
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,390
bakit naman

65
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:57,770
♪ Madaling tinatangay ng hangin ♪

66
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,630
Bakit mo ako ginaganito?

67
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:57,360
Chun'er.

68
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,550
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin

69
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:01,280
♪ Sino ang mananatiling kalmado ♪

70
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,870
na ikaw ay anak ng Empress?

71
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:03,200
Bakit mo ako hinayaang mamatay mag-isa?

72
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,460
♪ At huwag kang matakot? ♪

73
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,500
♪ Isang bahagyang ripple ♪

74
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,600
Alam mo bang galit ako sayo?

75
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:07,080
Galit ako sayo!

76
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:09,270
♪ Ang lumulutang na buhay ay nakasabit sa isang sinulid ♪

77
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,080
-Chun'er!
-I hate you!

78
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,670
Galit ako sayo!

79
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:09,320
Chun'er!

80
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,270
Galit ako sayo!

81
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:12,920
♪ Habang hinihila, mas lumalambot ♪

82
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,200
Chun'er!

83
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:11,840
Chun'er!

84
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,550
Chun'er.

85
00:09:13,890 --> 00:09:16,740
♪ Sino ang maglakas-loob na magsabi ng forever? ♪

86
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:20,770
♪ Hayaan mo na ♪

87
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,850
Isa kang pinapaboran na anak ng langit,

88
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:25,280
♪ Mga sama ng loob at biyaya
ay hindi kailanman sinadya upang maging ♪

89
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,480
isang marangal na Prinsesa.

90
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:26,600
Hindi ka dapat kasali
sa labanang ito.

91
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:28,770
♪ Bakit kailangan mong kumuha at humingi ng labis? ♪

92
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:29,870
hindi ko sinabi sayo
dahil gusto kitang protektahan.

93
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,780
♪ Maghabi ka ♪

94
00:09:31,110 --> 00:09:36,060
♪ Mga dakila at maluwalhating dahilan ♪

95
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,720
Gusto kita

96
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,280
upang mamuhay ng masaya,

97
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:39,330
♪ Magkaharap kami ♪

98
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,710
kasiyahan, at magandang kapalaran.

99
00:09:39,350 --> 00:09:43,210
♪ Ang malakas na bagyong magkasama ♪

100
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:47,090
♪ Kahit sobrang sakit ♪

101
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:51,890
♪ Hindi man lang kami kumikibo ♪

102
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:52,670
Ako...

103
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:55,160
♪ Bakit sa mundong ito ♪

104
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,870
hindi nakarating sa...

105
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:59,670
♪ Ang pinakamatibay na puso
at pinakamalakas na kaluluwa ♪

106
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,080
sabihin mo...

107
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,390
kahit ano.

108
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,840
Chun'er.

109
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:10,390
nandito ako.

110
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,510
Hindi ako nakarating sa...

111
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,840
hindi nakarating sa...

112
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,120
Mga bantay!

113
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:21,000
Chun'er, gising ka na.

114
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:24,010
Partikular na nagkaroon ako ng isang tao
maghanda ng Dew Lotus Soup.

115
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,120
Naalala ko paborito mo yun.

116
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,620
Sa mga hapon ng tag-araw,

117
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,130
lagi kang may mangkok.

118
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,720
Pakinggan ang aking mga utos!

119
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,240
Ang bruhang ito ay pinangalanang Chu Qiao.

120
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,150
Siya ay isang kriminal na alipin ni Great Yong.

121
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:07,240
Ginaya niya ang Faceless Saintess

122
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,910
at naghimagsik laban sa Dakilang Yong.

123
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:12,960
Ngayon, sa harap ng Jiuyou Platform
sa Jinsheng Palace,

124
00:12:13,310 --> 00:12:15,770
susunugin siya ng buhay
bilang babala sa publiko!

125
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:24,600
Yan Xun.

126
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,000
Tulad ng sinabi ko sa iyo,

127
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:28,710
ang lugar na ito ay nagtataglay ng napakaraming masamang alaala.

128
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,500
Mas mabuti kung hindi ka sumama.

129
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,550
Ngunit hindi ka nakinig

130
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:33,880
at nagpumilit na sumama.

131
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:39,870
Makatitiyak ka,

132
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,080
ayaw mo ba ng tulong ko?

133
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:46,790
Nainform na ako
Kanyang Kamahalan ang Ikalabintatlo.

134
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:48,000
Kapag namatay na si Chu Qiao,

135
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,910
papahiram kami ng tropa

136
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,910
ng mga imperyal na guwardiya ni Zhenhuangcheng

137
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,640
para tulungan kang bawiin si Great Yan.

138
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,660
Salamat, Prinsesa Chun'er,

139
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,010
at ang Kanyang Kamahalan ang ikalabintatlo.

140
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,550
Yan Xun,

141
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,440
nagsinungaling ka sa akin.

142
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,000
Lumapit ka sa akin,

143
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,480
hindi para manghiram ng tropa.

144
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:51,600
Magsalita.

145
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,610
Saan nakakulong si Chu Qiao?

146
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,670
hindi ko alam.

147
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:03,410
Nakulong siya sa doghouse
ng Ikalabintatlong Prinsipe.

148
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:36,940
Ang antidote para sa pulbos na pampalambot ng kalamnan.

149
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,540
Ang pangalan ko ay Chu Qiao.

150
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,600
Dati akong alipin sa Great Yong,

151
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,600
at ngayon ako ang Reyna ng Ximeng.

152
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,510
Kilala ko itong si Chu Qiao.

153
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,970
Dati siyang alipin sa Qingshan Manor

154
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:10,510
at kalaunan ay tumalikod kay Great Yong.

155
00:15:13,630 --> 00:15:15,160
Zhao Chun'er at Zhao Yang,

156
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:17,480
kasama ang bruhang si Jia Meng,

157
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:20,640
ginamit ang Faceless God Sect
para apihin ang mga karaniwang tao.

158
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,270
Lahat ng kilos nila

159
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:24,000
ay naglalayong isama si Ximeng.

160
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:26,000
totoo ba ito?

161
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:27,480
Paano nangyari ang ganoong bagay?

162
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,720
Ang kasalukuyang Ximeng

163
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,720
ay isang bagong mundo.

164
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,270
Walang alipin doon,

165
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:34,120
at walang walang ingat na makakatapak sa

166
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,750
ang buhay at dignidad ng iba doon.

167
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,720
Bawat karaniwang tao

168
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,750
mabubuhay ng patas sa mundong ito.

169
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:42,030
Ang ganitong Ximeng ay hindi
maging dependent sa Great Yong,

170
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:44,430
ni hindi ito mag-uugnay kailanman
kasama si Great Yong!

171
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,600
Inalis na ni Ximeng ang pang-aalipin?

172
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,200
Hindi mo pa alam diba?

173
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,840
Narinig ko na maraming alipin
mula sa ating Dakilang Yong

174
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,970
tumakas sa Ximeng.

175
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,730
Nitong mga nakaraang araw,

176
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,920
sa pamamagitan ng pagbibigay sa akin ng buntot ng kuneho

177
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:58,030
at pinapakain ako ng lotus soup,

178
00:15:58,030 --> 00:15:59,290
maganda ang pakikitungo mo sa akin.

179
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:02,000
Para ba sa plano ngayon ang lahat?

180
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,120
Ang Jiuyou Platform na ito

181
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:09,310
ay umangkin ng 16 na kaluluwa ng pamilya Yan.

182
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,600
Si Chu ang huling mahalagang tao sa akin

183
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,960
sa mundong ito.

184
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,600
Hinding hindi ko hahayaang magdusa siya

185
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,790
ang pinakamaliit na pinsala dito.

186
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,200
Yan Xun.

187
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,550
Mayroon ka bang

188
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,840
hindi kailanman pinagsisihan ito?

189
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,600
Patayin mo na lang ako.

190
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,900
Ang ama ng aking anak
ay pinatay mo,

191
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:48,040
at namatay din ang nanay ko dahil sayo.

192
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:49,750
Sa mundong ito,

193
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:51,240
wala na akong natira.

194
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,820
Bakit hindi mo tapusin ang buhay ko
gamit ang sarili mong mga kamay?

195
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:58,840
Sa ganitong paraan, wala na akong sakit

196
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:01,320
o mga kalakip.

197
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,400
Chun'er.

198
00:17:20,069 --> 00:17:20,750
Chun'er.

199
00:17:21,349 --> 00:17:22,000
Chun'er.

200
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,160
Chun'er.

201
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:29,790
Yan Xun.

202
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:32,350
Chun'er.

203
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:34,750
Chun'er.

204
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,070
Lahat ng mga bagay na ito
ay ginawa ni Zhao Chun'er,

205
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:40,310
kasama ang pagdadala
ang Faceless God Sect.

206
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,970
Ngayong patay na ang mamamatay-tao,

207
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,400
pwede ba ako pumunta?

208
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,830
Hindi ba ako makakapunta?

209
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,070
tumahimik ka.

210
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,560
Mabilis, iligtas ang Prinsesa!

211
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:27,830
Ang paghawak sa isang prinsipe na bihag ay isang malaking krimen.

212
00:18:27,830 --> 00:18:29,070
Kung may hindi pagkakaunawaan

213
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:31,330
sa Ximeng, Great Yan, at Great Yong,

214
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:34,210
maaari nating ibaba ang ating mga armas
at pag-usapan ito.

215
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:36,200
Ngunit kung pipilitin mong lumaban,

216
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:38,730
ibig sabihin
paggawa ng isang kaaway ng Great Yong.

217
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:39,510
Chu.

218
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,850
Huwag maniwala sa kanila.

219
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:44,750
Ganyan sila nanloko
ang pamilya Yan noon.

220
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:45,950
Kung hahayaan natin si Zhao Yang,

221
00:18:46,510 --> 00:18:47,960
mamamatay pa rin tayo.

222
00:18:48,350 --> 00:18:49,790
Qingshan Manor, pakinggan ang aking mga utos!

223
00:18:49,790 --> 00:18:53,190
Kunin ang Hari ng Dakilang Yan
at Chu Qiao nang buong lakas!

224
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,130
Sino ang mangahas!

225
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:57,400
Zhuge Yue,

226
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,810
makipagtulungan sa akin.

227
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,890
Sabay tayong aalis dito.

228
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:08,790
Zhuge Yue.

229
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,510
Binigyan kita ng choice minsan.

230
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,950
Gusto kong umalis ka kasama ko.

231
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:16,110
Ikaw mismo ang sumuko sa landas na iyon.

232
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:17,510
Ngayon,

233
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:21,110
Ako si Zhuge Yue, Chief ng Qingshan Manor.

234
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:22,400
nagsisinungaling ka.

235
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:24,960
Bumalik ka lang sa Qingshan Manor

236
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:26,160
para iligtas ako.

237
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,480
Zhuge Yue,

238
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,460
sabay tayo.

239
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:33,230
Mali ka.

240
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,200
Kahit wala ka,

241
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,400
ang dugo ng pamilya Zhuge

242
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,070
dumadaloy pa rin sa mga ugat ko.

243
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:41,720
I'm destined to belong to
Qingshan Manor sa buong buhay ko.

244
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:43,250
Dapat may malinaw na linya

245
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,240
sa pagitan mo at ako.

246
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:58,640
Zhuge Yue,

247
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,960
