Hindi ko naisip iyon.

482
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:18,800
Ikaw noon

483
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:21,800
sinong nagsabi sa akin na huwag tanggapin ang aking kapalaran

484
00:34:22,150 --> 00:34:23,840
sa pinakamadilim na panahon ng aking buhay.

485
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,550
Binago mo ang aking kapalaran

486
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:28,010
at ang mga tadhana ng marami pang iba,

487
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:31,120
kabilang ang mga tao ng Ximeng.

488
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,600
Nagdala ka ng sinag ng liwanag

489
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,670
sa madilim na mundong ito.

490
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,510
Kahit malabo,

491
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:41,050
sapat na para mapanood ito ng maraming tao

492
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:42,440
at patuloy na mabuhay.

493
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:02,190
Noong maliit ako,

494
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:03,890
sa bawat sakripisyo,

495
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:07,320
Tumayo ako sa pinakalikod.

496
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:25,190
Lagi kong pinangarap na makalapit

497
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,000
upang tingnang mabuti

498
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:30,670
sa mga portrait at memorial tablets

499
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:32,960
ng mga ninuno ni Great Yong.

500
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:36,000
Hanggang ngayon,

501
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:39,630
Makakalapit na ako

502
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:43,290
at makakita ng malinaw sa unang pagkakataon.

503
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:53,310
Huan Huan.

504
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:56,100
Magkapareho kami ng background.

505
00:36:57,360 --> 00:37:00,400
Wala sa amin ang proteksyon
ng mga magulang mula pagkabata.

506
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:02,660
Kinailangan naming ipaglaban ang lahat sa aming sarili.

507
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:05,020
Siguradong maiintindihan mo ako.

508
00:37:07,630 --> 00:37:08,510
alam ko.

509
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:11,100
Nang walang proteksyon ng mga magulang

510
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:13,110
at umaasa sa iyong sarili sa lahat ng paraan,

511
00:37:13,110 --> 00:37:14,970
ito ay dapat na lubhang mahirap.

512
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:29,190
Huan Huan.

513
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:33,090
Ginugol ko ang kalahati ng aking buhay sa larangan ng digmaan

514
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:36,110
at hindi kailanman naakit sa isang babae,

515
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:37,760
hanggang sa nakilala kita.

516
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,480
Kung payag ka

517
00:37:48,110 --> 00:37:50,240
upang kumatawan sa 13 tribo ng Great Yan

518
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,290
at hindi gumawa ng isang kaaway ng Great Yong,

519
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,770
Mahusay Yong at Mahusay Yan

520
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,630
ay titigil sa apoy magpakailanman.

521
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,990
Tapos yung mga nakaraang hinaing

522
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:01,070
maaari ding isulat.

523
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:05,630
Ngunit...

524
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,070
Huan Huan.

525
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:18,440
Hindi ako isang taong mahilig sa pagpatay at digmaan.

526
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:21,110
Sana Mahusay Yong at Mahusay Yan

527
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:24,150
maaaring mamuhay nang payapa.

528
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:27,110
Sana mas makasama ka pa.

529
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,550
Huan Huan.

530
00:38:57,110 --> 00:39:00,240
Siguradong magiging ako
ang master ng Zhenhuangcheng.

531
00:39:10,070 --> 00:39:10,800
Ano ito?

532
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:13,530
Ito ay isang item
ng Great Yong royal family.

533
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,150
Ang bawat prinsipe ay may isa,

534
00:39:15,990 --> 00:39:19,100
dala ang kanyang sariling natatanging pattern
at ang kanyang ranggo.

535
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:23,040
♪ Ang alikabok sa mundo ♪

536
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:23,920
binigay ko sayo.

537
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:27,040
♪ Madaling tinatangay ng hangin ♪

538
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:29,190
Ito ba ay isang tanda ng pag-ibig?

539
00:39:27,740 --> 00:39:30,540
♪ Sino ang mananatiling kalmado ♪

540
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,960
Ito ang interes sa asno na iyon.

541
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:32,720
♪ At huwag kang matakot? ♪

542
00:39:32,750 --> 00:39:34,760
♪ Isang bahagyang ripple ♪

543
00:39:34,950 --> 00:39:38,540
♪ Ang lumulutang na buhay ay nakasabit sa isang sinulid ♪

544
00:39:38,820 --> 00:39:42,190
♪ Habang hinihila, mas lumalambot ♪

545
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:46,000
♪ Sino ang maglakas-loob na magsabi ng forever? ♪

546
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:50,040
♪ Hayaan mo na ♪

547
00:39:50,070 --> 00:39:51,190
Tapos yung asno ko

548
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:54,550
♪ Mga sama ng loob at biyaya
ay hindi kailanman sinadya upang maging ♪

549
00:39:53,630 --> 00:39:54,890
ay masyadong mura, hindi ba?

550
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:58,040
♪ Bakit kailangan mong kumuha at humingi ng labis? ♪

551
00:39:58,420 --> 00:40:00,050
♪ Maghabi ka ♪

552
00:40:00,380 --> 00:40:05,330
♪ Mga dakila at maluwalhating dahilan ♪

553
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:06,230
Huan Huan,

554
00:40:06,250 --> 00:40:08,800
♪ Magkaharap kami ♪

555
00:40:07,140 --> 00:40:09,020
Gusto kitang makasama habang buhay.

556
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:12,670
♪ Ang malakas na bagyong magkasama ♪

557
00:40:13,830 --> 00:40:16,560
♪ Kahit sobrang sakit ♪

558
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:21,350
♪ Hindi man lang kami kumikibo ♪

559
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:24,590
♪ Bakit sa mundong ito ♪

560
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:29,400
♪ Ang pinakamatibay na puso
at pinakamalakas na kaluluwa ♪

561
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:36,490
♪ Magbigay nang napakadali sa banayad na init? ♪

562
00:40:37,090 --> 00:40:39,880
♪ Minsan naming nakita ♪

563
00:40:39,910 --> 00:40:43,310
♪ Isang mirage sa lupa ♪

564
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:47,670
♪ Ang kagandahan ay hindi kailanman ♪

565
00:40:47,700 --> 00:40:52,430
♪ Tumatagal nang matagal ♪

566
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:56,220
♪ Kahit paano inukit ang jade ♪

567
00:40:56,240 --> 00:41:00,680
♪ Bato lang ♪

568
00:41:00,970 --> 00:41:08,180
♪ Mawawala rin ito sa wakas ♪

569
00:41:09,090 --> 00:41:20,860
♪ Mawawala rin ito sa wakas ♪

570
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,440
Zhao Che,

571
00:41:36,510 --> 00:41:37,630
gusto talaga kita.

572
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,610
Ngunit ako ay ipinanganak sa Great Yan,

573
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:43,380
nakatadhana na maging isa sa kanila sa buong buhay ko.

574
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,760
Hindi ko kayang bitawan si Great Yan

575
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,010
at sumali sa Great Yong.

576
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,660
Treat natin kagabi

577
00:41:50,190 --> 00:41:52,150
bilang isang magandang panaginip.

578
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,610
Sa muli nating pagkikita,

579
00:41:55,630 --> 00:41:57,960
ikaw ang magiging Crown Prince
ng Great Yong,

580
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:00,330
at ako ay maaari lamang maging Heneral Huan
ng Great Yan.

581
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:02,880
Pag nagkita tayo sa battlefield,

582
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:04,540
hindi na kailangang magpakita ng awa.

583
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:25,320
Nangako ka sa akin noon

584
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:27,880
na hindi mo papayagan si Chu Qiao
makagambala sa aming plano.

585
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:30,000
Tanggalin ang kasamaan
at sirain ang mga walang galang!

586
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:31,260
Kung hindi ka aalis ngayon,

587
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,070
hindi ka makakaalis.

588
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:35,320
Pagkatapos ay salamat, Young Master Zhuge.

589
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:37,400
Hindi ka mamamatay kung wala ang utos ko!

590
00:42:37,510 --> 00:42:38,630
Sinabi mo sa akin

591
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:40,480
na basta inalagaan kong mabuti si Chu,

592
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,670
babalik ka sana.

593
00:42:44,030 --> 00:42:44,760
Huan Huan.

594
00:42:45,070 --> 00:42:46,920
Kunin kaagad ang Hari ng Dakilang Yan.

